OL,3,C'It's killing me': Man living with
OL,4,Cfive stone lump desperate to get it
OL,5,Cremoved
OL,7,FA 48-year-old man living with a 30kg
OL,8,Flump on his body, which he cannot get
OL,9,Fremoved, has told ITV News Central the
OL,10,Fordeal is "killing him".
OL,12,FAlan Bromyard, from Long Eaton in
OL,13,FDerbyshire, first developed health
OL,14,Fproblems after undergoing weight loss
OL,15,Fsurgery at the advice of doctors in
OL,16,F2020.
OL,18,FHe now has a chronic condition called
OL,19,FLymphoedema which causes swelling in
OL,20,Fthe body's tissues and has been living
OL,21,Fwith the lump for two years.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
