OL,3,C'It's killing me': Man living with
OL,4,Cfive stone lump desperate to get it
OL,5,Cremoved
OL,7,FThe condition is caused by your
OL,8,Flymphatic system not working properly,
OL,9,Fwhich is the system that fights
OL,10,Finfection and removes fluid.
OL,12,FMr Bromyard told ITV News Central:
OL,13,F"From that two years to now it's been
OL,14,Fgrowing and growing, it's started off
OL,15,Fas a little orange and is now nearly
OL,16,F30 kilograms".
OL,18,FThe NHS won't fund his surgery to
OL,19,Fremove it because they say the surgery
OL,20,Fis considered cosmetic.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
