OL,3,C'It's killing me': Man living with
OL,4,Cfive stone lump desperate to get it
OL,5,Cremoved
OL,7,FMr Bromyard has been rejected twice by
OL,8,Fthe Derby and Derbyshire integrated
OL,9,FCare Board who have said an
OL,10,F"exceptional" reason is needed to fund
OL,11,Fthe surgery.
OL,13,FHe said: "I need to get someone in the
OL,14,FNHS to do something.
OL,16,F"I have no life at the moment. I've
OL,17,Fgone from running my small pedigree
OL,18,Fherd of cattle to having to get rid of
OL,19,Fthem because I can't work them.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
