OL,3,C'It's killing me': Man living with
OL,4,Cfive stone lump desperate to get it
OL,5,Cremoved
OL,7,F"I've had two stays in hospital with
OL,8,Fsepsis. I nearly died twice. Second
OL,9,Ftime I was on the floor for nine
OL,10,Fhours. I don't want there to be a
OL,11,Fthird time."
OL,13,FHe also used to enjoy fishing
OL,14,Falongside his role as a self employed
OL,15,Ffarmer but is now unable to work.
OL,17,FAlan contracted sepsis in August 2023
OL,18,Fand was in hospital for two weeks,
OL,19,Fwith six days in intensive care.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
