OL,3,C'It's killing me': Man living with
OL,4,Cfive stone lump desperate to get it
OL,5,Cremoved
OL,7,FThe fire brigade had to get him out of
OL,8,Fan upstairs room to take him to
OL,9,Fhospital and he was lifted out of his
OL,10,Fhome with a hoist.
OL,12,F"I have no life, my life is from the
OL,13,Fbed, to the kitchen and back, that's
OL,14,Fit."
OL,16,FBecause of his lump, he now spends all
OL,17,Fof his time in one room and sleeps
OL,18,Fdownstairs.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
