OL,5,Cremoved
OL,7,FHe said: "Everyone that's seen me, the
OL,8,FGP, surgeon, dietician, physio and
OL,9,Flymphoedema clinic all say it needs
OL,10,Fcutting off."
OL,12,FHis surgeon is supporting the need for
OL,13,Fsurgery, in a process known as a
OL,14,Fapronectomy which is a surgical
OL,15,Fprocedure to remove skin from the
OL,16,Flower abdomen.
OL,18,FHe has started a GofundMe page to help
OL,19,Fraise the money needed for the surgery
OL,20,Fand has raised #1,000 so far but still
OL,21,Fneeds around #2,500.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
