OL,7,F"Some treatments are not normally
OL,8,Favailable on the NHS and in these
OL,9,Fcircumstances people are able to
OL,10,Frequest individual funding requests
OL,11,Fwhere a service, intervention or
OL,12,Ftreatment falls outside of existing
OL,13,Fservice provision.
OL,15,F"The application for funding is made
OL,16,Fby the patient's clinician who is
OL,17,Frequired to demonstrate that the
OL,18,Fcircumstances are exceptional.
