OL,7,F"This decision-making process ensures
OL,8,Fthat each request is considered in a
OL,9,Ffair and transparent way, with
OL,10,Fdecisions based on the best available
OL,11,Fevidence and in accordance with our
OL,12,Findividual funding request policy."
OL,14,FMr Bromyard said he is now planning a
OL,15,Fthird appeal with hopes that his
OL,16,Fapplication will be accepted.
